
lineinfile      -   to modify/insert a line 
blockinfile     -   to insert/update/delete block of lines.

dest / path     -   in latest version, use path.
backup          -   to get backup and useful if any failures. 
marker          -   default BEGIN and END added as part of changes and can be override using marker.


To insert at end of file: 

    dest: file/to/path 
    block: | 
        statements

By default, bloc inserted at end of line. 

